## 9. Multi-IDE Coordination

### Understanding the Environment

This repository has multiple IDE worktrees:

| IDE | Folder | Branch | Purpose |
|-----|--------|--------|---------|
| **Cursor** | `_worktrees/cursor/` | `cursor-dev` | Your workspace |
| Antigravity | `_worktrees/ag/` | `ag-dev` | Off-limits |
| Agent | `_worktrees/agentx/` | `agentx-dev` | Off-limits |
| Manual | Root folder | `main` | Protected |

### Integration Point

All IDE branches merge into `develop`:

```
cursor-dev  ──┐
              ├──> develop ──> main
ag-dev      ──┤
              │
agentx-dev  ──┘
```

### Coordination Rules

- Each IDE works independently in its worktree
- Integration happens via PRs to `develop`
- Never directly interact with other IDE's worktrees
- Conflicts are resolved in `develop`, not in individual worktrees

